title: Bobby Talks About His Dog’s Surgery Complications + Best Slogans Draft + Amy And Lunchbox Are In A House Buying War

description:
Bobby gives an update on his dog Stanley who had to undergo four surgeries yesterday. We draft the best company slogans. Plus, we found out that the house Amy had been looking to buy…turns out Lunchbox is looking at the same house!
